properties.Title: Rooster and Owl
properties.Description/Notes: An A&J all-time favorite restaurant, Rooster and Owl serves a shared plates tasting menu with a focus on seasonal produce and global influences. We are proud to have discovered it before it was cool - it receively received one Michelin star.

properties.Title: Compass Rose

properties.Title: Ice Cream Jubilee
properties.Description/Notes: Our favorite ice cream shop in the city (or anywhere!). Creative hand-made flavors with seasonal specials that are always outstanding. Also happens to be woman- and AAPI-owned and involved in local advocacy!
